#Scoreboard fillers
scoreboard players set .1 skywars -3
scoreboard players set .2 skywars 9
scoreboard players set .Timer skywars -4
scoreboard players display name .1 skywars ["",{"text":" "}]
scoreboard players display name .2 skywars ["",{"text":" "}]
scoreboard players add .Timer timer 1

